<br>
 We arent getting anywhere. Melee classes are getting more damage for less delay with every expenssion, they can get 40% haste on a RBB, weapons that can do damage by spells built into them, and have the opportunity to never stop doing damage with a cleric in the group. The caster classes most benefiting from this are of course #1 clerics, #2 enchanters, #3 shamans. What group would take a level 60 wizard who needs to med half the time when they can have a level 60 rogue that can double back stab for 600 or more?  The best groups ate the higher levels are of course the ones made up of an enchanter for haste, buffs, and crowd control, and clarity to keep the clerics mana up. A cleric to keep all the tanks nice and in health and to give them crazy hp and ac buffs. And last, tanks to unleash none stop damage as long as the cleric can heal them, in addition to be able to take damage.<br>
<br>
   Why can casters getting better equipment such as spell haste?!?!?!  Why has spell haste never come to the attention of Verent before, if tanks can improve there hits by 40% + why cant there be equipment that does that for use. Or a bracer that reduces the use of mana by 20%, wouldnt that set the score right?  Verant has the ability to do this but it wont. Wizards are not the only class suffering either; mages, and necros are to but i think it hits wizards most of all because atleast they have melee power with there pets doing a good portion of the damage.<br>
<br>
 And now Verant wants to make the wizard the TP bitch. What am i suppose to do with all my time i put into my 55 wizard so far, stand at near KC and shout &quot;tping to just about everywhere for 25 pp!&quot;? Well thank you for caring so much, i think all of you play warriors and rogues.<br>
  Your options right now if you want to make eq any better is to wait until Verant makes some changes which i doubt will ever happen or start a rogue or some other melee class, after all you can twink a melee class like crazy, since when has your level one wizard casted a spell for 20 damage or ever will?<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
 Boycot now !!!!!<br>
 whose with me? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=nouseformana>Nouseformana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 2<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/5/01 7:20 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: IC, SS, and VF</span><hr size=1> please ignore my MANY spelling errors, i was in a fast train of thought :P <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/ufusionforcewiz.showPublicProfile?language=EN>FusionForceWiz</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br>  Posts: 37<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/6/01 12:43 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: IC, SS, and VF</span><hr size=1> arge  i tired of Grimstaff always fighting for the newbies.<br>
